1.Download Quran file from https://github.com/skillhacker-code/KindleQuran/blob/main/Al%20Qur'an%20Arabic%20Personal%20-%20Allah.kfx

Copy this file to Kindle device Document folder 

2. Download Quran Word by word dictionary from https://github.com/skillhacker-code/KindleQuran/blob/main/QuranDictionaryv2.mobi

Copy this file to dictionaries folder in kindle 

Set the font for Quran as publishers font in Kindle Device . 

When Highlighting the word select dictionaries and then select My Quran to English dictionary .

Then you can use Quran Word by Word Dictionary . 

If there is any errors please let me know . 

I made this for my own use , then thought of sharing this 
